'''碘化氰'''是一种无机化合物，化学式为ICN。这是由[[拟卤素|拟卤素]][[氰|氰]]和碘形成的化合物。它是有毒的白色挥发性晶体，与水缓慢反应生成[[氰化氢|氰化氢]]。<ref name=Bak>{{ OrgSynth | author = Bak, B. | author2 = Hillebert, A. | year = 1952 | collvol = 4 | collvolpages = 207 | volume = 32 | pages = 29 | title = CYANOGEN IODIDE | prep = cv4p0207 }}</ref><ref name=Lan1>{{cite journal | title = CYANOGÈNE Action de l'iode sur une solution concentrée de cyanure de potassium | author = Langlois, M. | journal = Comptes Rendus | volume = 51 | pages = 29 | year = 1860 | url = http://gallica.bnf.fr/ark:/12148/bpt6k30082/f29.table | access-date = 2011-05-27 | archive-date = 2016-02-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160208080819/http://gallica.bnf.fr/ark:/12148/bpt6k30082/f29.table | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name=Lan2>{{ cite journal | title = Ueber die Einwirkung des Jods auf concentrirte Cyankaliumlösung | author = Langlois, M. | journal = Annalen der Chemie und Pharmacie | volume = 116 | issue = 3 | pages = 288 | year = 1860 | doi = 10.1002/jlac.18601160303 | url = https://zenodo.org/record/1427157 }}</ref>

==制备==
它可以通过在冰水中混合I<sub>2</sub>和[[氰化物|氰化物]]（通常是[[氰化钠|氰化钠]]）来制备。这种物质可以用[[乙醚|乙醚]]来萃取。<ref name=Bak/><ref name=Lan1/><ref name=Lan2/>
:I<sub>2</sub> + CN<sup>-</sup> → I<sup>-</sup> + ICN

==应用==
由于其毒性<ref name=Poh>{{cite book | author = Pohanish, R. P. | title = Sittig's Handbook of Toxic and Hazardous Chemicals and Carcinogens | edition = 6th | chapter = Cyanogen iodide | year = 2011 | page = 808 | publisher = Elsevier | isbn = 978-1-4377-7869-4 | chapter-url = https://books.google.com/books?id=RYt0Wzb60b4C&pg=PA808 | access-date = 2021-03-10 | archive-date = 2017-04-17 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170417084522/https://books.google.com/books?id=RYt0Wzb60b4C&pg=PA808 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，碘化氰可用于剥制术中的防腐剂<ref>{{cite encyclopedia | title = Cyanogen halide | encyclopedia = Encyclopædia Britannica (online) | year = 2012 | publisher = Encyclopædia Britannica Inc. | url = http://www.britannica.com/EBchecked/topic/147758/cyanogen-halide | access-date = 2012-04-12 | archive-date = 2012-01-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120102022308/http://www.britannica.com/EBchecked/topic/147758/cyanogen-halide | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name=Poh/>。

==历史==
碘化氰于1824年由法国化学家{{le|Georges-Simon Serullas}} (1774–1832)首次制备。<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Serullas|title=Nouveau composé d'iode, d'azote et de charbon ou cyanure d'iode|journal=Annales de Chimie et de Physique|date=1824|volume=27|page=184–195|url=https://babel.hathitrust.org/cgi/pt?id=hvd.hx3dwb;view=1up;seq=188|series=2nd series|trans-title=New compound of iodine, nitrogen, and carbon, or cyanide of iodine|language=fr}}</ref>

==危害==
碘化氰在吸入或摄入时有毒，如果通过皮肤吞咽或吸收，可能会致命。 碘化氰可能导致抽搐、瘫痪和呼吸衰竭而死亡。碘化氰是一种强烈的刺激物，如果接触，可能会对眼睛和皮肤造成灼伤。 如果加热碘化氰至分解，它会释放有毒的[[氮氧化物|氮氧化物]]，氰化物和碘化物气体。碘化氰还会和酸、碱、胺和醇。ICN 会和水或二氧化碳反应，形成[[氢氰酸|氢氰酸]]。<ref name=Poh/><ref>{{cite web | title = Iodine cyanide - Compound Summary (CID 10478) | url = https://pubchem.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/summary/summary.cgi?cid=10478 | work = PubChem | publisher = NIH | access-date = 2021-03-10 | archive-date = 2014-01-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140104001958/http://pubchem.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/summary/summary.cgi?cid=10478 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="CDC">{{cite web | title = Iodine Cyanide; International Chemical Safety Card No. 0662 (U.S. National Version) | publisher = National Institute for Occupational Safety and Health, Centers for Disease Control and Prevention | year = 2005 | url = https://www.cdc.gov/niosh/ipcsneng/neng0662.html | access-date = 2012-04-12 | archive-date = 2018-04-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180406040233/https://www.cdc.gov/niosh/ipcsneng/neng0662.html | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="Chemical">{{cite web | title = Cyanogen Iodide | url = http://www.chemicalbook.com/ChemicalProductProperty_EN_CB3345368.htm | publisher = ChemicalBook | access-date = 2021-03-10 | archive-date = 2018-08-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180809015536/http://www.chemicalbook.com/ChemicalProductProperty_EN_CB3345368.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref>

